################################################################################
# <<4>> Gulch brainstorming area
################################################################################
# -- Unique rare maps: --
# These should only have one map each at weight 10, with very few of these
# guests of two or three of the given boss type. They don't have to randomize
# the water / scrap / mould placement, and can instead try to match the monsters
# with other wall tiles as is appropriate.
#  * ironbound beastmasters + entropy weavers
#  * green death + deep elf demonologists
#  * death knights + merfolk impaler draugr
#  * extra formless jellyfish + spectral kraken
#  * acid blobs + 1 eye of draining
#
# -- Branchform --
# If this were to become a branch, with these layouts converted to endvaults,
# it'd be in a roulette with Crypt. The current transient mutations would be
# moved to mutagenic stairs, and the more mundane animal guests would try to
# reach the variety of zombies by coming in bands with possessive sludge: it'd
# hide in non-chaotic monsters to make them berserk and get AF_CURARE melee
# bonuses (disappearing when giving the buff and reappearing when their host is
# slain). Work on extended and other gods almost certainly comes first, though.
################################################################################
